HEADWORD: Untrusser
<hw>Un*truss"er</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who untrussed persons for
the purpose of flogging them; a public whipper.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
